sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Exchange as Exchange Company
    participant Scarb as Scarb Prover (Relayer)
    participant Starknet as Starknet (On-Chain)
    participant User as Auditor / User
    
    Exchange->>Scarb: 1. Submit Wallet Balances & Liability Data
    Note over Scarb: 2. Generate Liability Merkle Tree Hash
    Note over Scarb: 3. Run Cairo circuit to Generate STARK Proof
    Scarb->>Starknet: 4. Submit STARK Proof & Root Hash to Registry
    Note over Scarb,Starknet: Relayer pays gas fees for transaction
    Starknet-->>Exchange: Transaction Confirmed (Proof Published)
    
    User->>Starknet: 5. Fetch Public STARK Proof & Root Hash
    User->>User: 6. Run STARK Verification locally
    User->>Exchange: 7. Request personal Merkle Branch
    User->>User: 8. Verify Merkle Branch Inclusion
